{"tid":81220,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"買 Wii U 定 Switch ?","createTime":"2017-01-15T07:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T06:11:02.000Z","uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5291d1a7959e7cc7253878cfe3a8e349d6f01659","tid":81220,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"之前我問過好多人, 都勸我唔好買 Wii U, 話冇咩玩. 講緊嘅係仲未公佈 Switch 嘅時候. 我當時咁問法係因為我睇上咗 Pikmin 3, Star Fox Zero, Splatoon, Super Mario Maker. 偏偏前兩隻都冇係 Wii 度出過.<br />\n<br />\n正當我諗住等個價再跌多陣先買嘅時候, 你 Switch 同我講會出 Mario Kart 8 Deluxe. 即係 Switch 會好似 Wii 嗰時咁出翻啲 GameCube Game? 咁仲買唔買 Wii U 好呢? 其實 Wii U 啲 Game cut 咗Game Pad 𠴱 Part 係咪會冇咩影響?"},{"pid":"a9bdb6285f38a1d15cc6e9804947e9b56a5152dd","tid":81220,"uid":19365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"Pikimin3同STARFOX zero感覺上未必會翻出響Switch，想玩返可以執部平既二手玩既，但感覺未必值得去買部全新，始終之後已經無game會出"},{"pid":"6f97a4142ae0aeba2d4edcb52285425ba2ad2a3e","tid":81220,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pikimin3同STARFOX zero感覺上未必會翻出響Switch，想玩返可以執部平既二手玩既，但感覺未必值得去買部全新，始終之後已經無game會出</blockquote><br />\n官方講明話唔再出 Wii U Game? 但我Googe到話 &quot;Nintendo denies it is ending Wii U production &quot; <a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2016/11/02/nintendo-to-end-wii-u-production/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Ftechnology%2F2016%2F11%2F02%2Fnintendo-to-end-wii-u-production%2F&d=YyJV2okEaSWCeIsyrmcBL0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=0b7db56d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2016/11/02/nintendo-to-end-wii-u-production/</a><br />\n<br />\n我本身係 Star Fox Fans, 而家搞到唔知買唔買 Wii U 好"},{"pid":"bb898b25e92f9260989f3128cdfee48843bda71f","tid":81220,"uid":19365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Pikimin3同STARFOX zero感覺上未必會翻出響Switch，想玩返可以執部平既二手玩既，但感覺未必值得去買部全新，始終之後已經無game會出</blockquote><br />\n官方講明話唔再出 Wii U Game? 但我Googe到話 &quot;Nintendo denies it is ending Wii U production &quot; <a href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2016/11/02/nintendo-to-end-wii-u-production/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Ftechnology%2F2016%2F11%2F02%2Fnintendo-to-end-wii-u-production%2F&d=YyJV2okEaSWCeIsyrmcBL0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=0b7db56d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/2016/11/02/nintendo-to-end-wii-u-production/</a><br />\n<br />\n我本身係 Star Fox Fans, 而家搞到唔知買唔買 Wii U 好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n官方講就咁講，但發售表已經幾乎空左<br />\nStarfox 0評價好似麻麻"},{"pid":"ac6eea64285c8bcf56610acaa5e0afe4e3f471f0","tid":81220,"uid":39065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:11:58.000Z","msg":"係黑洞裡面得閒到可以打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"65169322a4367c26a7d4cad1a09fe7e712a5ee52","tid":81220,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n都係諗緊買部二手wiiu定switch 同女朋友打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2b0ca24c2ba6be72476397ddfed15626f78195","tid":81220,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T09:34:34.000Z","msg":"switch 遲D 可能有 MH系列 ."},{"pid":"edc77c7b86a710e82d1daeb26e5e5c033bb9575b","tid":81220,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T20:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8960b87744abc9b81cf1c54a35fee1e1105095f","tid":81220,"uid":43304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T20:59:10.000Z","msg":"我有買star fox zero<br />\n我覺得幾好玩, 關卡設計好tight好刺激<br />\n好多人話control 難同埋其他新載具無聊<br />\n如果比較為返64, 咁都係嘅....搞啲新野又無大improve 到<br />\n<br />\n但係作為fans, 有成套新野玩已經好enjoy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有新鮮感都重要. 下下拎舊作比較, 唔通永遠都重玩64 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最難頂都係個畫面. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個年代咁嘅畫面係唔合格! 其他wiiu game 邊會咁核突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n買wiiu 定switch好. <br />\nwiiu 個library 齊晒, zelda mario pikmin DK乜都有<br />\nparty game 又有好幾隻, 係屋企同人玩一定夠game<br />\n<br />\nswitch 新野一定無咁多game 住, 唔急咪買左wiiu 先囉<br />\n留番splatoon, mario kart 到遲下想買switch 先買"},{"pid":"c4d467473edacff26873aa72b98181fc93a0a1cc","tid":81220,"uid":39200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T01:29:27.000Z","msg":"老任官網寫左 Wii U '近日生産終了予定'<br />\n<br />\n如果部 2 手 Wii U 係光碟頭無壞、無被鎖機一切正常運作，可以考慮入手<br />\n<br />\nSwitch 個首發陣容唔係好多，唔一定要衝首發，反而 Wii U 真係有唔小好 Game 被埋沒左"},{"pid":"ef468da12cee4b6acd4eb0a049b5675be6ba8680","tid":81220,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c8da657a6721e6d363add227aa2717cc4cd32f","tid":81220,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"連登比唔比討論二手買賣?<br />\n<br />\n比既話 我有部美版黑色wii u賣<br />\n<br />\n有興趣就講聲 無就由佢"},{"pid":"946c64d198d8be91eefbb1bd666ef40b9972715a","tid":81220,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"wii u 係未鎖區？"},{"pid":"40aea902ded5fbd4b659f10f562c89ce3279904b","tid":81220,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2aa3250f8cc06586d5cc03b7a6f00793767ced","tid":81220,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"Wii u唔係出咗好多年架喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似係vita嗰期，仲有人玩/買？<img src=\"/asset